{"tid":1932180,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓市疫境】利嘉閣：平均成交呎價1.44萬　較歷史高位累跌7.4%","createTime":"2020-03-18T14:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T07:39:05.000Z","uid":101341,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d2987058328117ff7e40b02e8d11cdceb7a57692","tid":1932180,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:42:05.000Z","msg":"「新冠肺炎」疫情持續，但在二手業主加大減幅，刺激二月下旬交投量大增，利嘉閣地產總裁廖偉強估計，三月份情況相若，料成交量大升，惟樓價續跌。<br />\n<br />\n他指，2月份全港50個指標屋苑的加權平均實用呎價再度回落，報14,441元，較一月的14,696元下跌1.7%，為5個月以來最大單月跌幅，並創過去13個月新低。若與去年五月時的歷史高位15,593元比較，樓價累跌7.4%。<br />\n<br />\n當中，新界區21個指標屋苑實用呎價跌2.1%，報12,199元，成為跌幅最大的地區；九龍區21個指標屋苑實用呎價報15,499元，按月跌1.8%；至於港島區8個指標屋苑的實用呎價跌幅則相對輕微，跌0.5%，報18,395元。"},{"pid":"184100148d6a29285f883d244bc6a2765cc146a7","tid":1932180,"uid":23160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:43:13.000Z","msg":"7%叫跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb5ce3a45b5e00a7179d4f47cec23eae92f8bbb","tid":1932180,"uid":189157,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:43:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母就算半價都係買唔撚起<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c4c98e48fca06343b67fe3f0c0dc7ee0b4cc7b","tid":1932180,"uid":13308,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:45:37.000Z","msg":"SARS到依嫁升撚左成幾倍回果7%就嘈?<br />\n跌70%都仲係高過SARS果陣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d1f4d3c3183449f2fe41c9d81f62bd3cf77b1a","tid":1932180,"uid":19092,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"184100148d6a29285f883d244bc6a2765cc146a7","tid":1932180,"uid":23160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T14:43:13.000Z","msg":"7%叫跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" c